        public boolean getBoolean(float probablilty)
        If the package is not enabled, returns false. If it is enabled, returns a boolean with a given probability of being true. The probability is a float from 0.0f to 1.0f, with 0 being no chance of returning true and 1 being a 100% chance of returning true.
